data.description: Welcome to this bright and charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom raised ranch with a walk-out basement, privately located on a cul-de-sac in Elk Creek Highlands neighborhood. The circular drive beyond the trees creates a beautiful setting as you approach the home. This single-family home is on a 1-acre lot and is surrounded by panoramic mountain views, Aspen and Pine trees. Enjoy the views and wildlife outside from the upper-level wrap around deck that has new composite decking and the wood pickets have been replaced with cable on the back side. At the front corner of the home there is a covered gazebo built into the deck that will be a favorite relaxation spot. The main living area with vaulted ceilings and wood burning stove, features an open concept living, dining, kitchen space that is perfect for entertaining. Meal-prep will be enjoyable in the updated kitchen with granite counters and newly installed open shelving. Escape to the primary bedroom that is its own, lovely retreat with a sitting area and updated bathroom. Another 3/4 bath and bedroom are on the main level. The fully finished walk-out basement offers a living/rec/combo space, two bedrooms, a 3/4 bath and a spacious laundry room. Looking for storage? The 2-car garage is oversized and there is a large storage building in the back yard. Starlink is the internet provider and seller says they have the high speed and it's "super-fast." The septic is 1250 gallons. Trash and Recycling is with Mountain View.
